# Final Project

## Repository
<https://github.com/sxb220276/Programming-Final-Project/tree/main>

## Description
This will be a simple game of snake with hopes to learn and potentially push it a little further 
with a brief, unexpected narrative.
This will require using all knowledge taught over the course's span in order to create it.

## Features
- Game of Snake
	- Simple system w/ player controller and point collection.
- Moving narrative
	- Creating checks in game to see if player has completed hidden goals.
- Interesting Visuals
	- Using subversion of the expected.

## Challenges
- Pygame basics of creating a player controller.
- creating different scenes and transitioning between them.
- Learning classes and "self"

## Outcomes
Ideal Outcome:
- Fully functioning game with all narrative intact, very little bugs

Minimal Viable Outcome:
- Basic game of snake

## Milestones

- Week 1
  1. Basic score system
  2. Player controller

